text: Lenino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Tabun- Aralsky Selsoviet of Yenotayevsky District, Astrakhan Oblast, Russia. The population was 895 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 100 km from Astrakhan, 41 km from Yenotayevka. == References == Category:Rural localities in Yenotayevsky District
title: Lenino, Astrakhan Oblast
